title: Kong Ai Vegetarian Centrum
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Filipino
description: Asian fusion vegetarian cuisine without garlic or onion. Food is all vegan. The only non-vegan item is ice cream. Also sells vegetarian frozen food including faux ham, nuggets, patties, plus dry goods including vegetarian oyster sauce, TVP, Meat Magic, vegetarian seasonings.
